snippet: Jamie Donaldson of Wales won his first European Tour title Sunday by shooting a six-under-par 66 to clinch a four-stroke victory in the Irish Open at Portrush, Northern Ireland.
abstract: Jamie Donaldson wins the Irish Open, marking his first European Tour victory; other golf results noted.
lead_paragraph: Jamie Donaldson of Wales won his first European Tour title Sunday by shooting a six-under-par 66 to clinch a four-stroke victory in the Irish Open at Portrush, Northern Ireland.

headline.seo: Jamie Donaldson Wins Irish Open by 4 Shots
